-- Verify it was added with the special alias
\d+ test_cagg_rt
                                                           View "public.test_cagg_rt"
                           Column                           |           Type           | Collation | Nullable | Default | Storage | Description 
------------------------------------------------------------+--------------------------+-----------+----------+---------+---------+-------------
